### CREATE A NEW GAME FROM A LOBBY

POST http://localhost:3000/lobbies/{{lobbyId}}/start-game
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### GET A LOBBY WITH GAME INFORMATION

GET http://localhost:3000/lobbies/{{lobbyId}}/with-game
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### GET A SPECIFIC GAME BY ID

GET http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### GET A GAME BY LOBBY ID

GET http://localhost:3000/games/lobby/{{lobbyId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### JOIN A GAME WITH A SPECIFIC COLOR

POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "color": "RED"
}

### SET PLAYER READY STATUS

POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/ready
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "isReady": true
}

### ROLL DICE

POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/roll-dice
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### MOVE A PIECE

POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/move-piece
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "pieceId": 0,
  "diceValue": 6
}
